DC.desc: The datacenter code for the NDT.

PROPERTY.desc: The property group that the network is being deployed for ie. hotmail = hot.

AGG_INSTANCE_NUM.desc: The instance number of the aggregation switches.

L3AGG_PREF.desc: Layer 3 aggregate routing naming scheme (A/B will be appended to the end automatically).

LB_PREF.desc: Load balancer naming scheme (A/B will be appended to the end automatically).

L3AGG_SKU.desc: Layer 3 aggregate routing hardware platform sku ie.(Nexus 3064X).

LB_SKU.desc: Load balancer hardware platform sku ie.(F5 Bigip 8950).

BE_TOR_SKU.desc: BackEnd top of rack switch hardware platform sku ie.(Nexus 3048).

XE_TOR_SKU.desc: XE top of rack switch hardware platform sku ie.(Nexus 3048).

TOR_OOB_SW_A.desc: *TYPING INPUT INTO THIS BOX WILL REPLICATE TO THE OTHER OOB TOR TEXTBOX. TOR x34b 01a OOB switch

TOR_OOB_SW_PORT_A.desc: *TYPING INPUT INTO THIS BOX WILL REPLICATE TO THE OTHER OOB TOR PORT TEXTBOX. TOR x34b 01a OOB switch port
